        {
            "id": 6020500,
            "title": "《A股動向》隆基綠能:BC電池組件效率突破26%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><tr></tr></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:601012:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/601012\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">601012-CN</a>)宣布,經美國國家可再生能源實驗室(NREL)權威認證,其自主研發的大面積(260.9平方厘米)晶硅-鈣鈦礦兩端疊層太陽電池轉換效率達33%,刷新全球大面積疊層電池效率紀錄。同時,BC電池組件效率突破26%,推動晶硅組件效率極限向27%以上邁進。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　　隆基綠能今日收升0.14%,報14.74元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>。(jq)</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6020500",
